description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Suspense / Charles Burton Barber
-A Special Pleader / Charles Burton Barber
-A Monster / Charles Burton Barber
-No Ride Today / Charles Burton Barber
-The Nut Gatherers / William-Adolphe Bouguereau
-A Childhood Idyll / William-Adolphe Bouguereau
-The Song of the Lark / Sophie Gengembre Anderson
-The Time of the Lilacs / Sophie Gengembre Anderson
-Girl with Doll / Fritz Zuber-Buhler
-Reclining Beauty / Fritz Zuber-Buhler
name: Masterpieces of World  - Girls in the Paintings -
